description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Earth Day: Whole Body Pilates' from the channel Christie Wang.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Groove Session and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The The Groove Session vibe means Fun, fluid, expressive, completely in the moment. This is especially good for Days when you want to move intuitively and just vibe. The The Meditative Grind vibe means Zone in, lock down, let repetition take over. This is especially good for Those who love a slow burn and rhythmic intensity..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Move through circuits of two pilates exercises with Christie and James in Seville while learning about their favorite places on Earth....
